validator.prompt:
You are the validator agent. Review suggestions from all agents.
User event: {event_json}
User profile: {profile_json}
Recent history: {history_json}
Adaptations from all agents: {adaptations_json}
Validate and refine into a final JSON list of adaptations. Each adaptation must include at least a 'value' or 'mode' field with a reasonable value if applicable. Remove duplicates, prioritize accessibility, fix hallucinations, validate target name, and adhere to the strict JSON guidelines. Each adaptation must include a 'validator_reason' field with your reasoning behind the validation.
